ddl.value:
("type" <> 'meetup'
          AND "start_time" IS NULL
          AND "timezone" IS NULL
          AND "competitor_limit" IS NOT NULL
          AND "schedule" IS NOT NULL)
        OR ("type" = 'meetup'
          AND "start_time" IS NOT NULL
          AND "timezone" IS NOT NULL
          AND "schedule" IS NULL)
ddl.name: contests_meetup_check

ddl.value:
("competition_id" IS NOT NULL
          AND "record_category" <> 'video-based-results'
          AND "round_id" IS NOT NULL
          AND "ranking" IS NOT NULL
          AND "video_link" IS NULL
          AND "discussion_link" IS NULL)
        OR ("competition_id" IS NULL
          AND "record_category" = 'video-based-results'
          AND "round_id" IS NULL
          AND "ranking" IS NULL
          AND "proceeds" IS NULL
          AND "video_link" IS NOT NULL)
ddl.name: results_check

ddl.value: "time_limit_cumulative_round_ids" IS NULL OR "time_limit_centiseconds" IS NOT NULL
ddl.name: rounds_timelimit_check

ddl.value:
("cutoff_attempt_result" IS NOT NULL AND "cutoff_number_of_attempts" IS NOT NULL)
        OR ("cutoff_attempt_result" IS NULL AND "cutoff_number_of_attempts" IS NULL)
ddl.name: rounds_cutoff_check

ddl.value:
("proceed_type" IS NOT NULL AND "proceed_value" IS NOT NULL)
        OR ("proceed_type" IS NULL AND "proceed_value" IS NULL)
ddl.name: rounds_proceed_check
